SubjectRegulations Amending the Canadian Aviation Regulations (Various Subjects)
PrecisRegulations Amending the CANADIAN AVIATION REGULATIONS (VARIOUS SUBJECTS) in order to (1) codify global exemptions; (2) clarify regulatory text; (3) enhance alignment with international partners; and (4) address minor discrepancies between the English and French versions of the Regulations.
